snippet.title: Pair 2 Monsters To Make Bond With Each Others In This Adorable Monster-Matching Game | Monster Bonds
snippet.description:
Help the professor identify monsters by pairing 2 monsters bonding with each others, both monsters must be exactly the same or it won't work!

Like, Comment, and Subscribe if you like the video!

"Monster Bonds" by Daniel Moreno
https://daz.itch.io/monster-bonds
